Assuming fresh installation of ubuntu 16.04
1. Install nvm with the following command:
	curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.11/install.sh | bash
2. Close current terminal and open a new one.
3. Verify that nvm is installed with the following:
	command -v nvm
4. Install node with the following command:
	nvm install node
5. Install react, react-router, react-router-dom with the following command:
	npm install react react-router react-router-dom --save
6. Install ganache-cli with the following command:
	npm install -g ganache-cli
7. Install truffle with the following command:
	npm install -g truffle
